title: Lana Jewelry Diamond Upside Down Gold Hoop Earrings
description:
Take a fresh twist on a traditional hoop. Both feminine and flirty, these hoops exude undeniable confidence.  Made of 14-karat gold, with diamond accents. Designed by Chicago designer and founder of the luxe jewelry line Lana Jewelry, Lana Bramlette.   Go glam and channel  your inner celebrity!  

2 1/2 x 1 1/2 in.
